'''長毛犰狳'''（學名：''{{lang|la |Chaetophractus vellerosus}}''）是一種[[犰狳|犰狳]]。<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Luaces |first1=JP |author2=Ciuccio M |author3=Rossi LF |author4=Faletti AG |author5=Cetica PD |author6=Casanave EB |author7=Merani MS  |year=2011 |title=Seasonal changes in ovarian steroid hormone concentrations in the large hairy armadillo (''Chaetophractus villosus'') and the crying armadillo (''Chaetophractus vellerosus'') |journal=Theriogenology |publisher= |volume=75 |issue=5 |pages=796–802 |pmid=21247625 |doi=10.1016/j.theriogenology.2010.09.029}}</ref><ref name="Neotropics">{{cite book |title=Mammals of the Neotropics: The central neotropics: Ecuador, Peru, Bolivia, Brazil |last=Eisenberg |first=John Frederick |authorlink= |author2=Redford, Kent Hubbard |year=1999 |publisher=University of Chicago Press |edition=illustrated |isbn=978-0-226-19542-1 |page=101 |pages= |url=http://books.google.co.in/books?id=p2MDAzCeQQoC&lpg=PA101&dq=Screaming%20Hairy%20Armadillo&pg=PA101#v=onepage&q=Screaming%20Hairy%20Armadillo&f=false |accessdate=19 May 2011 |archive-date=2013-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021171839/http://books.google.co.in/books?id=p2MDAzCeQQoC&lpg=PA101&dq=Screaming%20Hairy%20Armadillo&pg=PA101#v=onepage&q=Screaming%20Hairy%20Armadillo&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>在[[南美洲|南美洲]]的中部及南部生活，慣於挖地洞，受驚時會發出尖叫聲。<ref name=iucn/><ref name="Neotropics"/>

本物種有兩個亞種，分別是{{r|ITIS_624896}}：
* Subspecies ''Chaetophractus vellerosus pannosus'' {{small|(Thomas, 1902)}}
* Subspecies ''Chaetophractus vellerosus vellerosus'' {{small|(Gray, 1865)}}：指名亞種。
2015年一項研究發現本物種的指名亞種跟[[密毛犰狳|密毛犰狳]]除了在體型上有些微差異，無論是[[形態學|形態學]]上從兩者的頭骨比較還是[[遺傳學|遺傳學]]上都無法分辨兩者{{r|iucn|iucn_old|Abba 2015|Gibb 2016}}。
因此，密毛犰狳很可能只是長毛犰狳的指名亞種的異名，而整個[[毛犰狳属|毛犰狳属]]亦很可能是一個[[多系群|多系群]]{{r|Abba 2015|Gibb 2016}}。[[IUCN|IUCN]]目前已刪了密毛犰狳的紀錄{{r|iucn_old}}。

